des:
Amazon Alexa and the KUMHO FILOS home products work together to help you control home appliance nice and easy.
You can simply ask Alexa to turn on, turn off or dim the light. 
There’s no need to go to the switch to adjust you home light - just talk to Alexa on your Amazon Echo, Echo Dot, Amazon Tap or Echo Show. 
After connecting Alexa to your KUMHO FILOS products in a few simple steps:
(1). Download our "KUMHO FILOS" app in android or ios app market;
(2). Register one KUMHO FILOS account in our "KUMHO FILOS" app;
(3). You need to have some KUMHO FILOS devices in hand;
(4). Configure these devices in our KUMHO FILOS" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "KUMHO FILOS" skills;
(5). Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android,ios or Amazon app market;
(6). Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
(7). Search "KUMHO FILOS" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
(8). Click Enable skill of "KUMHO FILOS", and you'll be navigated to KUMHO login page;
(9). Input your KUMHO account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
(10). Now all setup is finished. 

You can enjoy the voice control on your home devices like these:
"Alexa, turn on my livingroom light"
"Alexa, turn off my livingroom light"
"Alexa, dim my livingroom light"
"Alexa, brighten my livingroom light"
"Alexa, set the livingroom light to 20 percent"
